      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the whole congregation. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And so the New Testament passover, the Lord’s supper, ought not to be neglected by any that are capable of celebrating it. No ",
        "children": []
      },
