      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "that was ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "uncircumcised ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "might eat of it. Neither may any now approach the Lord’s supper who have not first submitted to baptism; nor shall any partake of the benefit of Christ’s sacrifice, who are not first ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "circumcised in heart. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Any stranger that was ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "circumcised ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "might eat of the passover, even ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "servants. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Here is an indication of favour to the poor Gentiles, that the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "stranger, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "if circumcised, stands upon the same level with the home-born Israelite; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "one law for both. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This was a mortification to the Jews, and taught them that it was their dedication to God, not their descent from Abraham, that entitled them to their privileges.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
